TY  - JOUR
T1  - A Control Problem of Bellman
AU  - Dantzig, George B.
Y1  - 1971/05/01
PY  - 1971
DA  - 1971/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.17.9.542
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.17.9.542
